  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age40-85 years

          -  Diagnosis of Spontaneous osteonecrosis of the knee (SONK)in last month, Stage 1 or 2
             by MRI.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Hyperbaric treatment (HBOT) in the last 2 years.

          -  Any contraindication for HBOT

          -  Pregnancy.

          -  Inability to sign inform consent

          -  Any contraindication for MRI
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
